*Dozvolu* im je dala njena majka. (Her mother gave them permission.)

*Dozvolu* za to nikada ne bih dao. (I would never give permission for that.)

Moj otac mi nikada ne bi dao *dozvolu* za to. (My father would never give me permission for that.)

Nema *dozvolu* za ulazak u sobu. (There is no permission to enter the room.)

*Dozvolu* da se to radi smatra se malo riskantnim. (Permission to do that is considered a bit risky.)